data.description: Beautiful home located in the town of Culpeper, near route 29 for easy commute. Just a short drive to downtown Culpeper for great shopping and dining, and Rockwater Park! The main level offers an entrance into the home's sitting room moving to the family room/kitchen combination. The kitchen flows into the family room and Dining area.  Recently replaced Dishwasher, Microwave, Range and Washer. The dining area is surrounded by many windows.  Staircase is split with a landing as you move to the 2nd floor, there are 4 bedrooms including the  primary bedroom on the upper level.  The primary bedroom has a large walk-in closet and a double sink bath with a jetted soaking tub and shower.  Down the steps to the basement is a recreation room and office alcove. Basement has a rough in for a full bath.  The rest of the basement offers plenty of storage.  Large backyard for outdoor play & enjoyment and a lovely back ground area.   Come to Culpeper!!
